    "body": "Another workaround with matplotlib 2.2+ is to use constrained_layout instead of tight_layout (https://matplotlib.org/tutorials/intermediate/constrainedlayout_guide.html) which seems to work fine and does not raise a warning in Jupyter notebooks."
